message.content:
I need to identify the line items and values related to costs incurred to secure customer orders and deliver goods and services.

In an income statement, these costs typically include:
1. Cost of Goods Sold (COGS) - the direct costs of producing goods that are sold
2. Selling Expenses - costs related to sales and marketing activities to secure customer orders

Looking at the income statement provided:
- Cost of Goods Sold: 504,930.00 (related to delivery of goods)
- Selling Expenses: 9,828.84 (related to securing customer orders)

Based on the example solution provided, it appears the task is specifically asking for the Selling Expenses value, which is the cost incurred to secure customer orders.
